Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,537)\fnI hate Comic Sans\b1\fscx120\c&HB42EBE&\fad(1000, 1000)}WHISPER OF THE HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need a bag for just milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They put it in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say 'no' ! Pour me some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, want some barley tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... I'll come there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. The word processor open?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still printing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should buy an electronic notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smoke too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've gone to your aunt's, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Shiho wears me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've got work tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll eat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The library's been busy changing to a bar-code system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the book-cards better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't right... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you leave out a line?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go first. I have to get this right or my prof will complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.80,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can read, but don't stay up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd seen that name before... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, too... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:48.04,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taken all these books out before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa Seiji... what's he like? Wonder if he's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.40,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0, 500)}Amasawa Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep in your clothes? Put the rice on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I've got to meet Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My purse... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ran back upstairs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try by the phone... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... where you left it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late! Lock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clumsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flying so low!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's a lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kosaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing weird, I hope... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you wait till school starts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've read all my books, and the public library's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reading 20 before school starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20? You've got high-school entrance exams, don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your card and the book card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever borrowed this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare. They don't even have it at the public library.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.84,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Donated - Amasawa's Collection
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Amasawa' ... Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who this 'Amasawa' is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look what you made me do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone gave it to us. I wouldn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask an older teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? I've been at the front gate since 11!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have to stand in the sun I get more freckles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, Harada. You take freckles too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a serious problem, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah... all right, out of here, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move up! Move up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried, but it's not going to work. Why not just sing it in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'White clouds spreading up over a hill... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'... a road winds up to the town.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'An old house with small windows... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'An old dog waits for me to come home... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Country road leading far away... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'The road to my old home town... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'West 'Ginia, my mother the mountain... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'My good old home town.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's trite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Concrete roads, everywhere... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cut down all the trees, filled in the valleys... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Western Tokyo... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Tama Mountain... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'My home town is concrete roads.'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's this 'problem' ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need the lyrics yet... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... are you in love with anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Studying for entrance exams would be easier having someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could encourage each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko! You're in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When? Who? Is he handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in another class. He's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet him, then! If you don't like him, just say no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's someone else you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hide it from me! Confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Su... Su... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me my bag, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue sports bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw it over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and go back to the bench!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm first-string, and we're through to the regionals!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with Sugimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do? The way I reacted, he might know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He's too dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the guy who wrote you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least your parents aren't always after you to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence isn't always great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my book! I'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You'll be late for cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That book... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, 'Tsukishima Shizuku' .
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My library card... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forget about 'Concrete Road' , though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! Jerk! Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'I'd forget about "Concrete Road"... '
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiho? You're back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a ride with someone who was coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer Intensive Seminar. Dad's at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could clean up a little... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wash the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku! The breakfast things are still out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's busy! We've got to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the rice and put away the washing. I'll take a shower and make dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aunt says come see her when you get into high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can take it easy just because Mom and Dad don't bug you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even wanted me to bring home soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your aunt, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same thing last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It was miso! Boy, was it heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two kilos of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku! Get up and vacuum by your desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm washing the sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And airing the bedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that stuff away and bring Dad his lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? You're going to the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I go instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll clean the toilet, the bath and the balcony and go to the Co-op?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to turn the bedding and fix dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mail these, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-A-I-L!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to read them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the paper-clip off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey cat... are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get off here. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! A cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The library's that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it felt just like the start of a story... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:14.37,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,No Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a hill! How far up is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he live around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cat! Where are you going? Do you live around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew there was a place like this way up here... 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going around teasing dogs isn't nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're teasing me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:23:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never guessed there was a store like this up here either... 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.32,0:24:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.42,0:24:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello... 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.93,0:24:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. Look around all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.27,0:24:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baron gets bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.61,0:24:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this doll 'the Baron' ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.57,0:24:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Baron Humbert von Jechingen. Quite the name... 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.21,0:25:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.92,0:25:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.80,0:25:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.42,0:25:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was sitting in some castle, all rusted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.26,0:25:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look... 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.74,0:25:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.15,0:25:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.75,0:26:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What great dwarfs!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.15,0:26:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a young lady who knows about dwarfs, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.66,0:26:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the face... if it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.76,0:26:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.76,0:26:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The light shines on the glass. Come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.86,0:26:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.23,0:26:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.91,0:27:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they live in different worlds. He's the king of the dwarfs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.92,0:27:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only while the clock is striking 12 is she changed back from a sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.09,0:27:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he appears every hour... 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.93,0:27:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... and waits for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.43,0:27:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The artist who made this must have been disappointed in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.19,0:27:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they both look so sad... 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.86,0:27:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This clock's fast, isn't it... 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.69,0:27:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only about five minutes, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.40,0:27:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.78,0:27:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to be at the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.95,0:27:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come back sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.62,0:27:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... but go left to get to the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.93,0:28:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right above it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.31,0:28:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a find! A place where stories start!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.61,0:28:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.65,0:28:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.24,0:28:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.78,0:28:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.83,0:28:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgetful, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.92,0:28:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks... but how... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.79,0:28:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.97,0:28:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cat! Is that your cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.18,0:28:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure eat a big lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.56,0:28:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.83,0:28:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Concrete roads, everywhere' ... 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.60,0:28:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not mine! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.36,0:29:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here you are... 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.03,0:29:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.82,0:29:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.16,0:29:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I'd found a treasure hidden in a cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.58,0:29:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what someone said buried me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.50,0:29:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.88,0:29:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting more books?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.47,0:29:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.05,0:29:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still at it? What about lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.64,0:29:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.72,0:29:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will? Thanks, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.25,0:29:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,June 16th... 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.71,0:30:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amasawa's read this one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.21,0:30:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.59,0:30:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He's not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.06,0:31:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.11,0:31:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.57,0:31:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.24,0:31:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain every day this term!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.81,0:31:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you're studying because you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.33,0:31:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.58,0:31:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Study hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.33,0:31:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.68,0:31:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.72,0:31:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.76,0:31:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! We'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.85,0:31:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate all these tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.02,0:31:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.32,0:31:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.69,0:31:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.86,0:31:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.20,0:31:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.28,0:31:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Maybe that's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.49,0:31:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.35,0:32:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.33,0:32:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.55,0:32:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up. Gather the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.23,0:32:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.90,0:32:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see Miss Kosaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.03,0:32:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go to the teachers' room first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.90,0:32:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.24,0:32:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.83,0:32:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.41,0:32:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lucked out on the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.70,0:32:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.16,0:32:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I studied was on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.25,0:32:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not just a baseball goof... 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.75,0:32:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko's good at guessing, too. Why not study with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.42,0:32:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Harada?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.97,0:32:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.42,0:32:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sugimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.68,0:32:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.60,0:33:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fixing me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.60,0:33:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.77,0:33:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never just guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.90,0:33:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.52,0:33:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.49,0:33:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A library-book donor? Gee, I don't know... 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.03,0:33:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you at lunch-time. There's this stamp in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.87,0:33:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.37,0:33:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Dr. Amasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.67,0:33:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've read it. It's a good book!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.17,0:33:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.46,0:33:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.80,0:33:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was chairman of the PTA a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.85,0:33:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The PTA? Would you know his given name?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.64,0:33:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His given name?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.44,0:33:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr Kimura, do you remember that Dr. Amasawa's given name?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.98,0:33:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Amasawa? It was 'Koichi' .
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.90,0:33:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa Koichi... 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.74,0:34:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His youngest son's in your year, Tsukishima. You don't know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.24,0:34:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.58,0:34:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.58,0:34:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.08,0:34:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.42,0:34:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.92,0:34:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.59,0:34:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.97,0:34:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.43,0:34:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.11,0:34:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.96,0:34:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ignored me! Of all the nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.26,0:34:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.18,0:35:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a jerk! He won't let me avoid him!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.81,0:35:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been carrying her lunch all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.98,0:35:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima with a boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.31,0:35:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like springtime has come for Shizuku at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.82,0:35:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.82,0:35:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You met a prince from one of your books?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.99,0:35:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.16,0:35:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to find out what he's like!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.83,0:35:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yuko, you heard his name. Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.83,0:35:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.00,0:35:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.84,0:35:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Ma', something, 'Masaki' , maybe... 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.88,0:35:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.51,0:35:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.51,0:35:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's like Tsukishima to run out without hearing the end of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.58,0:35:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know, but you don't... 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.18,0:35:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart beats in misery and ecstasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.52,0:35:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terribly romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.52,0:36:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really tease a girl who has just written your lyrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.86,0:36:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.65,0:36:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.03,0:36:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Shizuku! O great poet! We will not transgress again!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.37,0:36:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.88,0:36:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure... 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.92,0:36:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about old home towns, so I wrote about what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.38,0:36:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.76,0:36:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Country road, this old road... 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.22,0:36:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'If I go right to the end... 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.40,0:36:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Got a feeling it'll take me... 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.40,0:36:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'... to that town, country road.'
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.76,0:36:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good, Shizuku. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.62,0:36:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not hard to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.14,0:36:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.41,0:36:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can give this to the juniors and sing it at the teachers' thank-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.83,0:36:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.25,0:36:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.13,0:36:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.75,0:37:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'I left because I was alone and I had nothing... 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.13,0:37:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Pushed away my sadness and pretended I was strong... '
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.26,0:37:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies, the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.11,0:37:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.78,0:37:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.28,0:37:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the choir room! We'll show them your lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.11,0:37:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going to the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.62,0:37:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another test tomorrow... 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.12,0:37:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll study there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.62,0:37:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bookworm!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.41,0:37:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.33,0:38:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harada... 
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.33,0:38:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I talk to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.34,0:38:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.35,0:38:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have these flowers been watered?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.53,0:38:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron's gone... maybe someone bought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.73,0:39:00.06,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,World Emporium; Nishi Shiro, Prop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.42,0:39:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Nishi Shiro' ... maybe that jerk's name is 'Nishi' , too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.06,0:39:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku! Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.07,0:39:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko's on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.57,0:39:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go deaf, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.24,0:39:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.95,0:39:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.41,0:39:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.83,0:39:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.96,0:39:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not far.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.92,0:39:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.93,0:39:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.43,0:39:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.93,0:39:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.77,0:39:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.93,0:40:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who wrote the letter got Sugimura to ask me to answer it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.44,0:40:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh... 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.28,0:40:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you, of all people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.78,0:40:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.12,0:40:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is so dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.79,0:40:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't know how you feel about him... 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.96,0:40:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize to him. But I can't go to school tomorrow looking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.18,0:40:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And miss the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.97,0:40:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.81,0:40:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.54,0:41:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.21,0:41:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.67,0:41:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.04,0:41:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The library again, Shizuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.17,0:41:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Yuko's.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.34,0:41:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.85,0:41:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.02,0:41:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.07,0:41:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Harada... 
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.04,0:41:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... then she started crying. Did I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.09,0:41:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, ' Why you, of all people,' didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.22,0:41:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A guy on the baseball team asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.72,0:42:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.39,0:42:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't want to hear something like that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.39,0:42:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.39,0:42:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.10,0:42:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are dense, you know! She likes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.40,0:42:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No way! I don't need this!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.41,0:42:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't? How do you think Yuko feels?! She stayed home sick today!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.87,0:42:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.75,0:42:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.92,0:42:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make jokes at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.42,0:42:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.67,0:42:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've liked you for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.76,0:42:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.97,0:42:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like me? Or do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.51,0:42:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a boyfriend... 
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.77,0:42:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... 
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.44,0:42:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.44,0:42:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.77,0:42:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.11,0:42:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've always been friends... I like you, but not... 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.28,0:43:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I can't say what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.92,0:43:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.30,0:43:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.14,0:43:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.02,0:44:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.53,0:44:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The parcel delivery left this with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.53,0:44:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... again!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.28,0:44:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.55,0:44:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't eat all these ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.89,0:44:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're home... 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.39,0:44:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.31,0:46:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.98,0:46:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been shut out, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.32,0:46:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live here? Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.49,0:46:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not very nice. Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.58,0:46:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we change, I wonder? I was always so sweet... 
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.34,0:46:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Books don't even excite me like they used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.51,0:46:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always someone inside me saying, 'Things aren't that easy!'
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.01,0:46:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.04,0:47:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.58,0:47:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moon lets you pet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.05,0:47:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moon, you're not coming in?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.09,0:47:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.92,0:47:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.39,0:47:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I call him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.06,0:47:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.14,0:47:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't stay in one house.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.06,0:47:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard him called 'Ball' at one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.61,0:47:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's others.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.78,0:47:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he does the rounds... 
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.95,0:47:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! He commutes on the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.58,0:47:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.79,0:48:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, by himself! That's how I came here. I followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.92,0:48:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he brought me to a neat store, just like out of a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.25,0:48:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I insulted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.30,0:48:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said he wasn't very nice. Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.60,0:48:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not like Moon at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.14,0:48:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's half-devil, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.28,0:48:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.28,0:48:30.44,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you... 
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.95,0:48:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your grandfather sick? The store's been closed and I thought... 
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.12,0:48:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fine. It's a weird store. He doesn't open very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.29,0:48:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad he's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.29,0:48:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see Baron through the window. Did he sell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.29,0:48:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cat doll? You want to see it? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.18,0:49:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.66,0:49:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.51,0:49:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afraid of heights?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.68,0:49:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I like high places. This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.35,0:49:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the time it looks best.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.85,0:49:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.21,0:50:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.21,0:50:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.88,0:50:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clock's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.55,0:50:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.39,0:50:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa's delivering it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.39,0:50:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.39,0:50:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was here being fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.39,0:50:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.44,0:50:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took three years. He finished it the day you forgot your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.40,0:50:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.07,0:50:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it wasn't yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.90,0:50:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look into the cat's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.58,0:50:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick, before the light goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.38,0:51:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engelzimmer... 'angel's room' .
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.72,0:51:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The artisan accidentally scratched it with a cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.22,0:51:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.06,0:51:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baron won't go. He's a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.77,0:51:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.06,0:51:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means something to him. He won't say what, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.32,0:51:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look as long as you like. I'll be downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.08,0:51:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on the light if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.63,0:51:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird. I feel as if I've known you for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.97,0:51:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I really want to see you... 
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.77,0:51:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look sad today, somehow... 
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.33,0:52:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.17,0:53:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.17,0:53:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making a violin?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.34,0:53:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.51,0:53:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.52,0:53:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fits like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.52,0:53:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made all that? By hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.52,0:53:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.90,0:53:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.69,0:53:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shape hasn't changed in 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.07,0:53:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound comes from the craftsman's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.87,0:53:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made all those?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.91,0:53:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! There's a violin-making class here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.37,0:53:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one of them is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.54,0:53:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.05,0:53:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.71,0:53:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.05,0:53:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.82,0:53:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You made this? It's like magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.43,0:53:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you talk like that with a straight face?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.89,0:53:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? It's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.06,0:54:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.07,0:54:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.70,0:54:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can play, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.12,0:54:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.16,0:54:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play for me, okay? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.75,0:54:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen... 
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.96,0:54:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please please please!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.92,0:54:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to sing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.63,0:54:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I'm tone-deaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.13,0:54:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.11,0:54:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing. You know this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.51,0:55:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Had a dream of living on my own... 
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.48,0:55:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'... with no fear of being all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.86,0:55:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Pushed my sadness down inside of me... 
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.86,0:55:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'... and pretended I was strong as I could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.82,0:55:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Country road, this old road... 
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.33,0:55:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'If you go right to the end... 
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.00,0:55:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Got a feeling it'll take me... 
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.55,0:55:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'... to that town, country road.'
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.01,0:56:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'It doesn't matter to me how sad I might be... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.35,0:56:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'I will never ever let a tear show in my eye... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.57,0:56:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'If my feet are moving faster that's because I only want to... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.47,0:56:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'... push away memories... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.10,0:56:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Country road, this old road... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.75,0:56:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'... could go right to my home town... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.38,0:56:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'I won't go there, I can't go there... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.93,0:56:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'... can't go down that country road.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.56,0:56:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Country road, when tomorrow comes... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.11,0:56:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'I'll be like I always am... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.67,0:56:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Want to go back there, can't go back there... 
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.28,0:56:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Fare thee well... 
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.62,0:57:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'... country road.'
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.32,0:57:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.66,0:57:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukishima Shizuku. We met the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.29,0:57:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you'd come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.67,0:57:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my musical friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.80,0:58:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice singing. You're the lucky one who was there when he fixed the clock... 
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.56,0:58:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji has some pretty friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.98,0:58:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Seiji' ? Are you Amasawa Seiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.52,0:58:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... didn't I tell you my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.15,0:58:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It says 'Nishi' outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.40,0:58:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Grandpa's name. I'm Amasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.87,0:58:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! First I was buried alive, and now the sky's fallen in!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.37,0:58:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What difference does it make what my name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.00,0:58:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot! You've been calling me by my full name!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.55,0:58:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never asked me mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.71,0:58:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never had the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.22,0:58:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My image of Amasawa Seiji... 
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.55,0:58:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.55,0:58:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... was someone quiet and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.64,0:58:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You read too many books.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.98,0:58:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.12,0:59:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun. They're nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.62,0:59:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back. They'll like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.21,0:59:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to listen. Singing's too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.96,0:59:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're a good violinist. Is that what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.47,0:59:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots as good as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.97,0:59:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to do is make violins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.14,0:59:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... you're good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.48,0:59:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a school for it in Cremona, Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.48,0:59:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.48,0:59:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And not go to high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.94,0:59:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are dead against it. Grandpa's my only ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.46,0:59:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be great to know what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.72,1:00:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no idea at all. I just go from one day to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.97,1:00:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can go or not. I fight with my parents every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.64,1:00:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I go, I won't know if I have the talent until I try.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.65,1:00:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.19,1:00:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not far. See you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.32,1:00:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima... 
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.33,1:00:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.99,1:00:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a talent for poetry.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.50,1:00:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you sang back there was fine, but I liked 'Concrete Roads', too.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.17,1:00:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to forget that!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.17,1:00:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.84,1:00:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.34,1:00:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.68,1:00:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.70,1:01:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall asleep with the light on again.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.63,1:01:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you decide on your future?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.38,1:01:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.71,1:01:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your future!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.55,1:01:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't yours Suginomiya High?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.05,1:01:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.55,1:01:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at university finding that out.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.89,1:01:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.16,1:01:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's class is canceled so now she sleeps in!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.34,1:02:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.43,1:02:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run faster!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.43,1:02:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.46,1:02:23.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hour 1: Spare Period
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.11,1:02:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.95,1:02:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.78,1:02:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look awful!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.45,1:02:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure got better fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.29,1:02:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you were out with a boy last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.12,1:02:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.29,1:02:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little bird... who said you were like lovers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.17,1:02:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.81,1:02:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harada... I'll tell my friend the answer's no. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.31,1:03:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.31,1:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.22,1:03:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Sasuke on TV last night? It was great!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.29,1:03:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This formula will be on the mid-term, so remember it!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.34,1:03:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.02,1:03:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tsukishima here?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.19,1:03:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amasawa? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.36,1:03:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tsukishima in this class?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.70,1:03:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima? Yeah, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.87,1:03:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima! You've got a visitor!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.37,1:03:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A male!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.21,1:04:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.21,1:04:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.05,1:04:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.72,1:04:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.22,1:04:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishima's got a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.73,1:04:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.40,1:04:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.07,1:04:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Italy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.57,1:04:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.24,1:04:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.75,1:04:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.23,1:04:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.72,1:04:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.93,1:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't talk with all those people around.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.60,1:05:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I wanted to tell you first.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.60,1:05:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them think what they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.44,1:05:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad finally gave in. On one condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.78,1:05:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.95,1:05:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apprentice in a workshop there for two months.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.29,1:05:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.62,1:05:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who runs it is very strict. He'll see if I have talent or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.63,1:05:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also if I have the patience to stick it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.46,1:05:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise I go to high school.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.80,1:05:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that they're leaving an escape route... 
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.64,1:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... but it's a good chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.31,1:05:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.31,1:05:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I get my passport. Dad's talking to the school today.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.98,1:05:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, then... 
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.23,1:05:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Your dream's coming true.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.57,1:05:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll do the best I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.16,1:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.16,1:05:58.16,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... 
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.16,1:06:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain's stopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.83,1:06:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... 
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.50,1:06:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.17,1:06:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a rainbow... 
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.31,1:06:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Cremona like? I hope it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.48,1:06:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an old town, with lots of violin makers.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.03,1:06:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great. You're on your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.45,1:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.54,1:06:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping we'd go to the same high school... 
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.16,1:06:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid thing to think... 
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.48,1:07:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw your name on the library cards a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.90,1:07:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We passed each other in the library.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.28,1:07:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even sat beside you there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.45,1:07:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I read all kinds of books so my name would be on the cards before yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.54,1:07:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... 
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.17,1:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing your song to myself in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.68,1:07:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.18,1:07:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.10,1:07:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.07,1:07:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, she's mad!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.28,1:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.48,1:08:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.16,1:08:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.69,1:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.82,1:08:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished already?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.22,1:08:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm meeting Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.82,1:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're by the station, get some milk.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.33,1:08:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who drinks it all!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.50,1:08:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's slacking off these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.27,1:09:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.35,1:09:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make you skip cram school?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.36,1:09:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head's in a whirl.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.03,1:09:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.70,1:09:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.87,1:09:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.37,1:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.37,1:09:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.04,1:09:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad and I aren't speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.97,1:09:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.89,1:09:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he comes back to graduate, he goes again for ten years!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.64,1:09:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like forever!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.73,1:10:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's like fate brought you together! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.63,1:10:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too good to last. Two people read the same books... 
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.86,1:10:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... except one's going forward while the other stays behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.20,1:10:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... 
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.25,1:10:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinuyo was in his class for a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.00,1:10:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said he was hard to get to know, but good-looking and smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.92,1:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that, will you!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.93,1:10:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel worse!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.93,1:10:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? He likes you, doesn't he? He told you!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.43,1:10:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm not so sure... 
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.77,1:10:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it. I'd write every day... we'd encourage each other... 
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.78,1:10:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say 'go for it' to someone more ambitious than you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.53,1:10:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... 
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.49,1:10:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't understand what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.33,1:10:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you be in love without your future planned out?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.79,1:11:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.96,1:11:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the juniors liked your translation of 'Country Roads' .
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.30,1:11:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can express yourself, too... unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.89,1:11:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'There's lots as good as me' .
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.72,1:11:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.81,1:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to find out if he has talent. Well, so will I!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.40,1:11:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write a story!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.15,1:11:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one I want to write. If he can do it, so can I.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.99,1:11:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's exam time... 
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.49,1:11:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. Thanks, Yuko. I feel empowered.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.00,1:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You going?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.77,1:11:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.42,1:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.17,1:11:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell your mother hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.88,1:11:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go for it, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.89,1:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugimura will realize.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.60,1:11:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.60,1:12:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so easy! I just have to do something, too!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.69,1:12:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moon?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.16,1:12:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muta?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.04,1:12:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Muta's gone again!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.62,1:12:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muta!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.79,1:12:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Muta' ... 
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.90,1:12:31.84,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,'Whisper of the Heart' : Listen to the voice of the woods... 
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.49,1:12:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baron as the hero?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.83,1:13:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.08,1:13:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ask because Seiji says the doll is a treasure of yours... 
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.50,1:13:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to ask!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.84,1:13:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can. But on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.89,1:13:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.18,1:13:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you let me be the first person to read your story.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.68,1:13:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... 
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.85,1:13:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.52,1:13:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to? I don't know if I can write it or not... 
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.36,1:13:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for a craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.37,1:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect perfection at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.99,1:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let me show you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.21,1:13:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.72,1:13:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.31,1:14:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called 'mica slate' .
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.98,1:14:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the seam.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.73,1:14:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that... 
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.41,1:14:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.25,1:14:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called 'beryl'. You find it in emerald ore.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.50,1:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emerald? The jewel?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.50,1:14:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.40,1:14:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Seiji are like this stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.26,1:14:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rough, unpolished, still natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.85,1:14:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like stones that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.91,1:14:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But making violins, or writing stories, is different.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.69,1:14:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rough stone is inside you. You have to find it and then polish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.86,1:14:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes time and effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.53,1:15:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see the ore that makes up most of that stone?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.53,1:15:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.70,1:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could polish that, but what you'd get would be worthless.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.21,1:15:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smaller part inside is purer.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.04,1:15:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might even be a better stone deep inside where we can't see.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.38,1:15:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Old people like to preach.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.56,1:15:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared. What if there isn't a beautiful crystal in me?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.56,1:15:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to write. And you'll be the first one to see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.69,1:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'll look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.20,1:15:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rough stone... lapis lazuli... 
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.08,1:15:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go forth together... 
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.92,1:15:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... in search of the treasure of lapis lazuli!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.59,1:16:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have no fear. Space is deformed on the night of the new moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.10,1:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faraway things loom large, nearby things look small.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.36,1:16:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly! We will rise on the updraft.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.12,1:16:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make haste! The planetoids converge!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.05,1:16:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! We're riding the wind!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.55,1:16:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight up to that castle!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.30,1:16:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so high!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.93,1:16:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so high once you're there!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.62,1:17:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! When the air currents mingle in the afternoon, you can touch the stars!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.67,1:17:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.76,1:17:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rare! Shizuku looking at non-fiction... 
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.72,1:18:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's making a violin in his cell... 
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.71,1:18:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.92,1:18:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd left!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.42,1:18:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa said I might find you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.59,1:18:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.76,1:18:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow... 
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.93,1:19:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll wait here till you're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.80,1:19:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I can't walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.91,1:19:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.60,1:19:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't come to the airport, but I'll wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.64,1:19:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only two months.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.65,1:19:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm always so depressing. I'll do my best while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.00,1:19:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.50,1:20:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good trip!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.81,1:20:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luisa, my betrothed, and I were born in a distant land.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.70,1:20:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that town, magic still lived... 
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.20,1:20:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... and in the veins of its artisans flowed the blood of sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.21,1:20:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a poor doll-maker's apprentice who fashioned us... 
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.05,1:20:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... but Luisa and I were happy... 
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.39,1:21:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... because he had made us so we could love others.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.75,1:21:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then... 
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.90,1:21:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku... 
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.57,1:21:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.25,1:21:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.58,1:21:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I wasn't listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.09,1:21:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention! This is important!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.75,1:21:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.92,1:21:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harada, you read.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.76,1:21:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were up until 4 again?!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.60,1:21:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm not sleepy at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.39,1:21:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're spaced out all the time! Like just now... 
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.48,1:21:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking. I've got to organize what I want to write.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.11,1:21:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.48,1:22:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku? So you are home... 
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.81,1:22:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.48,1:22:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you could bring in the laundry!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.57,1:22:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.32,1:22:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku's here, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.29,1:22:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.52,1:23:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.30,1:23:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.86,1:23:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way... is anyone in the guidance office?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.03,1:23:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.20,1:23:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.87,1:23:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.88,1:23:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're home early, Shiho.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.34,1:23:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.88,1:23:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.05,1:23:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.05,1:23:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.22,1:23:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.56,1:23:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of moving out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.73,1:23:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found a place.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.40,1:23:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can you afford it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.90,1:24:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've saved from my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.41,1:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found another one at a cram school. I'll get by.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.58,1:24:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I've made you help me out too much around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.08,1:24:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.08,1:24:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will? Great!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.55,1:24:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money's tight till I graduate in the spring and get working... 
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.76,1:24:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... but I'll help you out then.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.93,1:24:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.93,1:24:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to go during your master's thesis... 
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.77,1:24:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.52,1:24:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You helped enough just with sorting out data.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.44,1:24:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Shizuku can concentrate in her own room. She's acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.99,1:24:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.61,1:24:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school called me. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.45,1:24:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.04,1:24:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone down a hundred places!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.29,1:24:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at her desk all the time... what's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.64,1:25:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.64,1:25:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.73,1:25:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.65,1:25:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What high school will take you with marks like this?!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.19,1:25:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to high school!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.55,1:25:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your head! What can you do with a middle-school education?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.66,1:25:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can decide my own future!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.33,1:25:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.71,1:25:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face the facts! The school makes its report on you after the second term!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.42,1:25:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fine one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.71,1:25:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't study! You just work part-time!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.84,1:25:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do what I have to!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.72,1:25:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who isn't doing that! Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.56,1:25:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something more important to do!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.35,1:25:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.69,1:26:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiho, Shizuku... that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.69,1:26:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Dad... listen to this girl!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.20,1:26:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you come out here and tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.87,1:26:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku, change out of your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.87,1:26:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.14,1:26:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Is it true what Shiho says?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.23,1:26:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do so care about my marks!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.56,1:26:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said you weren't going to high school.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.06,1:26:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said I wouldn't get into one!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.90,1:26:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiho... can Shizuku and I talk alone for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.53,1:26:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.12,1:26:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.41,1:26:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Tanakas.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.41,1:26:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.41,1:26:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.60,1:26:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your dad back?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.92,1:27:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come here, Asako? I've been hearing about Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.25,1:27:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.43,1:27:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Shizuku... 
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.27,1:27:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what you're doing now more important than studying?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.44,1:27:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me what it is?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.94,1:27:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's time.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.28,1:27:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this something you have to do right away?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.62,1:27:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only got three weeks left to do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.45,1:27:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm testing myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.29,1:27:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.62,1:27:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Testing yourself? How?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.80,1:27:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will we know if you don't say?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.97,1:27:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something you can't even tell us?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.30,1:27:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.31,1:27:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.11,1:28:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you're doing at the library, I admire how hard you're working.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.70,1:28:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let her do what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.89,1:28:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone has to be the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.17,1:28:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should know that if anyone does... 
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.09,1:28:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Shizuku, do what you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.47,1:28:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not easy when you walk your own road.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.35,1:28:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've only got yourself to blame.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.85,1:28:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And join us at mealtimes, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.02,1:28:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We're a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.03,1:28:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.53,1:28:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Shiho.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.20,1:28:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.70,1:28:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku... 
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.71,1:29:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what Dad said, but what he really wants is for you to study.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.46,1:29:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It's written on his face.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.55,1:29:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving out next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.63,1:29:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have your own room.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.55,1:29:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving home?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.39,1:29:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. So smarten up!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.53,1:29:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.53,1:29:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the one is real.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.24,1:29:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.77,1:29:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.26,1:31:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luisa... you've finally come... but I've grown so old... 
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.17,1:31:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku... 
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.71,1:32:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in... I was fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.18,1:32:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to bother you. I've brought my story.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.65,1:32:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finished?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.40,1:32:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised you'd be the first to read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.07,1:32:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a novel!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.30,1:32:24.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,'Whisper of the Heart'
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.16,1:32:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you read it now? I'll wait as long as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.08,1:32:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've worked so hard on it... shouldn't I take my time?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.59,1:32:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop if you don't like it. I hate to ask, but... 
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.76,1:32:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's pounding... 
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.72,1:32:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'll read it right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.56,1:32:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come sit by the fire. It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.82,1:32:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we won't be bothered.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.66,1:33:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I wait downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.91,1:33:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm not cold at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.79,1:33:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course... but... 
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.62,1:34:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asleep here?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.70,1:34:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku... I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.37,1:34:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. It's very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.87,1:34:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.88,1:34:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you really think! I couldn't write what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.71,1:34:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last half doesn't make sense. I know that!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.26,1:34:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... it's rough, blunt, unfinished... 
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.39,1:34:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... just like Seiji's violin.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.23,1:35:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've shown me the rough stone you've just cut out of the rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.23,1:35:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've worked hard. You're wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.45,1:35:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to rush now. Take your time and polish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.60,1:35:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out here. Come inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.94,1:35:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... 
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.67,1:35:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... now I've written it I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.28,1:35:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.94,1:35:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to learn more... 
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.78,1:35:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... but Seiji's getting further and further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.31,1:36:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that I had to force myself to write, and I was so scared... 
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.59,1:36:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like Seiji, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.07,1:36:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.82,1:36:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.82,1:36:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Seiji finished his first violin, we had ramen noodles.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.22,1:36:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumbo size.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.29,1:36:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.67,1:36:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where was I?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.67,1:36:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found the Baron in a coffee-shop... 
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.80,1:36:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, in Germany... 
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.64,1:37:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a student. He looked so melancholic... 
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.02,1:37:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked the owner to sell him to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.36,1:37:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.03,1:37:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baron had a lover, and he wouldn't separate them.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.53,1:37:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was waiting for her to come back from being repaired... 
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.04,1:37:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... at the doll-maker's shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.87,1:37:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like in my story!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.71,1:37:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... quite the coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.01,1:37:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to come home, so I'd just about given up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.59,1:37:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a lady friend of mine... 
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.22,1:37:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... said when the other doll came back she would take it... 
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.73,1:37:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... and bring the two dolls together.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.65,1:37:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the owner gave in.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.73,1:37:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up leaving Germany with just the Baron.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.70,1:37:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I promised her I'd come back, and asked her to keep the other doll.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.54,1:38:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day the dolls met again... 
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.25,1:38:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... would be the day we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.17,1:38:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then the war started, and I couldn't keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.26,1:38:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was finally able to go back, I looked all over for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.35,1:38:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was no trace of her, or the Baron's lover.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.86,1:38:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have been very important to you... 
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.53,1:38:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your story brought the Baron out of my memory and back to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.53,1:38:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes... 
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.67,1:38:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.14,1:38:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... 
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.30,1:39:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stone suits you perfectly. I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.39,1:39:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, finish up your story.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.23,1:39:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.75,1:39:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.42,1:39:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.26,1:39:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.93,1:39:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.85,1:39:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.60,1:39:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the bath. Where have you been till this hour?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.36,1:39:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I worried you. Today I return to studying for my entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.45,1:40:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your trials are over?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.45,1:40:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.77,1:40:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat? There's curry... 
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.29,1:40:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.29,1:40:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'For now' ... 
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.97,1:40:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku, the bath's open.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.20,1:40:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, a soldier at ease.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.14,1:41:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.07,1:42:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait there!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.00,1:42:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle! You're here!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.26,1:42:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.05,1:42:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an earlier plane. Hop on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.62,1:42:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... you'll be cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.60,1:42:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climb on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.02,1:42:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get a coat.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.40,1:42:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No time! Get on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.94,1:42:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.03,1:42:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was out there calling you in my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.04,1:42:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Shizuku!'
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.75,1:42:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you appeared!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.38,1:42:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a team!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.04,1:43:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too... it's like I'm still dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.55,1:43:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was Cremona?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.47,1:43:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot different than I thought. But I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.85,1:43:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting light!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.40,1:43:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I get off?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.66,1:43:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.74,1:43:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made up my mind I was going to ride you up this hill!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.00,1:43:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.46,1:43:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no man's burden!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.01,1:43:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be of use!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.51,1:43:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Push!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.43,1:43:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.99,1:44:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku! Jump on!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.22,1:44:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.39,1:44:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold the coat.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.68,1:44:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.90,1:44:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here... 
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.08,1:45:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! In the mist it looks just like the sea!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.92,1:45:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my secret place. It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.63,1:45:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to see this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.31,1:46:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.31,1:46:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything to help... I was just thinking of myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.98,1:46:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... you were the reason I did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.98,1:46:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I pushed myself. I understand myself better now.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.45,1:46:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to study hard and go on to high school.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.58,1:46:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Shizuku... 
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.41,1:46:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... I can't say how soon it'll be, but... 
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.75,1:46:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... would you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.05,1:46:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a violin maker... and then... 
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.77,1:46:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.93,1:46:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.44,1:46:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Great!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.86,1:46:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... it's cold... 
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.78,1:46:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku... I love you!
