Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.54,1:47:08.90,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,By myself, without feat
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.35,1:47:15.15,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed of going
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.79,1:47:21.38,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Shutting up my loneliness
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.38,1:47:26.96,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting my strong self, I'll go
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.96,1:47:30.14,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Country road
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.14,1:47:39.81,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,If you follow this road onward
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.81,1:47:46.11,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It continues to that town, I think
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.11,1:47:53.61,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Country road
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.97,1:48:03.43,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting tired of walking then standing still
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.43,1:48:09.76,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Floating closer, my hometown
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.76,1:48:15.83,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The uphill road winding around the hill
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.83,1:48:21.44,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scolding that me
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.44,1:48:24.62,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Country road
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.62,1:48:34.31,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,If you follow this road onward
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.31,1:48:40.66,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It continues to that town, I think
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.66,1:48:48.14,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Country road
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.95,1:49:23.08,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what discouraging times there are
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.08,1:49:29.08,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never show any tears
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.08,1:49:35.93,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Without heart, I'll hurry and set myself free
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.93,1:49:41.47,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get rid of my memories
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.47,1:49:44.71,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Country road
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.71,1:49:54.27,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this road continues to my hometown
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.27,1:50:00.80,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't go, I can't go
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.80,1:50:07.11,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Country road
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.11,1:50:10.37,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Country road
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.37,1:50:19.92,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, the me I always am
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.92,1:50:26.34,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back, but I can't, farewell
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.34,1:50:35.71,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Country road
